node.text: Thank you to everyone who came to the @windsorstore grand opening at San Antonio’s North Star mall! Your good energy, yellow outfits, eyeshadow looks using my palette, sea of merch in the line, gifts for Blue and Lola mean the world to me, you have no idea. This is a video my manager, @evegail24 (Major girl boss and CEO of @mattermediagroup ), took of a group of girls who drove 4 HOURS to see me for their friends birthday. They had matching shirts, papers for me to sign and were the absolute cutest. I wish I could individually post EVERY SINGLE PERSON that came to the meet and greet, but you guys would probably hate me. I rewatched this video a million times and smile every time. Thank you. From the bottom of my heart. I’m the most grateful girl in the world and don’t know what I did to deserve you guys. #GirlsSupportingGirls #Adelangels
